package.name: crazycodr/standard-exceptions
package.description: This project is aimed at providing additional standard exceptions to php. Many exceptions that are missing from the SPL are constantly being reproduced in different projects. By providing a package of high-quality, well organised exceptions, it will, in the long run, increase interroperability between projects.
